<br>
Here take this self-help test - which is IC and which is OOC?<br>
<br>
- Hello fair maiden, how are you. Do you by anychance know of a good inn nearby - I am weary of my journy from Qeynos and must rest the night before I head south to the fabled land of the trolls.<br>
<br>
- Hey man, are you camping the AC? I don't want to KS you and will respect it if you are.<br>
<br>
The first one is IC, the second is OOC. How did you score? If you didn't get that right, you might need some psychiatric help or at least some time off to go take a walk or something.<br>
